Malcolm Goodwin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Malcolm_Goodwin 0 Malcolm Goodwin (born November 28, 1982) is an American actor from Brooklyn, New York. He is perhaps best known for his appearance in the music video for the hit song "Party Rock Anthem." He also appeared as Seamus "Shea" Daniels on Breakout Kings, and as Clive Babineaux in iZombie.
